                        name="Accordion Item"
                        summary="Support for families"
                        text="&lt;ul>&#xa; &lt;li>Paid leave for new parents welcoming a child through birth, adoption, surrogacy or fostering&lt;/li>&#xa; &lt;li>Paid leave and support for people caring for sick family members&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li>&#xa; &lt;li>Support for family planning, including adoption and surrogacy assistance*&lt;/li>&#xa; &lt;li>Discounts at U.S childcare centers, plus access to an on-site daycare center at our headquarters in Lake County, IL&lt;/li>&#xa;&lt;/ul>&#xa;&lt;p>*Available in the U.S.&lt;/p>"/>
                    <accordion_item_4
