                        text="&lt;p>We partner with employees on their well-being journey, connecting them to tools, and support to help them be their best selves, at work and at home. Because when you're at your best, you can make the most impact.&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.abbvie.com/join-us/life-at-abbvie/well-being-in-the-workplace.html&quot;>Explore more&lt;/a>&lt;/p>"/>
